			<div class="content" id="post-content-1828123">
									

<p><strong>Escape from Site 19</strong> is an SCP Board Game that had been in development from May 2013. It is suitable for 3 to 5 players, recommended ages 18 and up.</p>
<p>It is an Extreme RPG board game where the players have to perform some quite unusual tasks - think a more exciting game of &quot;Activity&quot; or Jumanji - from the movie.</p>
<p>The main theme of the game is a catastrophical containment breach on Site 19. The players’ characters represent characters from the SCP Universe (Foundation and GOI alike), escaping from Site 19 or fulfilling their own agenda, dealing with the dangers of escaped SCP objects.</p>
<p>The goal of the game is to escape from the site, completing various game and real-life tasks tied to particular SCPs, and defeat one of the SCP-0001s at the end of the game, randomly chosen at the beginning.</p>
<p>I won't go into an elaborate rules explanation as they are still a subject to the betatesting, but that's the gist of it! There are over 350+ SCP objects included in-game.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.efs19.com">Check out our new web!</a></strong></p>
